Setup for the test case presented in Hsu and Farmer(1997) article.

For more details see "Benchmark Solutions of Radiative Heat Transfer Within 
Nonhomogeneous Participating Media Using the Monte Carlo and YIX Method".
doi: https://doi.org/10.1115/1.2824087

Replace the functions present in RTS_functions.f90 with those present in user_functions.f90

To facilitate post-processing, replace these lines in the output.rts file.

!===============================================================
!                     Lineup Variable Save               
!===============================================================
.true.   !on/off lineup save module (only for 3D simulations)
 1        !Method: 1-Point 2-Node
 2        !Number of Lineups
!---------------------------------------------------------------!
! Axis  >>   X:(x,a,b)   Y:(a,y,b)   Z:(a,b,z)                  !
!---------------------------------------------------------------!
!             CV Point         CV Node      Variable            !
! Axis      a        b        a       b        ID               !
!---------------------------------------------------------------!
   x      0.50d0   0.50d0     10      10        3 
   z      0.00d0   0.50d0     10      10        10
!===============================================================
